sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Angular Frontend
    participant B as .NET Backend
    participant V as Vector DB
    participant AI as OpenAI

    U->>F: UI Request
    F->>B: POST /generate-ui
    B->>V: Search relevant components
    V-->>B: Component metadata
    B->>AI: Structured prompt
    AI-->>B: Angular code JSON
    B->>B: Validate & sanitize
    B-->>F: Safe structured response
    F->>F: Render dynamically